snippet.title: Arcade Game: The Electric Yo-Yo (1982 Taito)
snippet.description:
A maze game where you guide your yo-yo to clear each level by collecting dots and avoidvng enemies.

Note: Cheats were used in the game and caused some graphical glitches.
